sentences.english: High wisdom aliens are also human being, they are not reach the level of God.

sentences.english: Sometimes these drugs can even get rid of the virus.

sentences.english: This overwrote everything including the BIOS settings in memory.

sentences.english: Fill a jewelry box with them. Wrap 'em up and present them to your partner.

sentences.chinese: 歐洲擁有153個名額，幷包括其第四名。

sentences.english: Highlight the key points and include the return on investment or loan payback requirements.
sentences.chinese: 重點突出關鍵要點，幷包括投資回報率和貸款回收期。

sentences.english: On the wedding night, Lin slept fully dressed and wrapped with a quilt.
sentences.chinese: 新婚之夜，林女士穿着全身的衣服幷包裹着一牀棉被。

sentences.english: This rare complication is reported and discussed after a review of literature.
sentences.chinese: 本文報告此罕見之幷發症，幷就有關文獻作一回顧。
